lead_paragraph: After two days filled with rain, the sun actually made an appearance at Wimbledon on Thursday, allowing for plenty of play all around the grounds, a chance to finally conclude the first round — and several surprises, the biggest of which was French Open champion Garbine Muguruza's exit.

headline.print_headline: Rain Gone at Wimbledon, but So Are Muguruza, 17 Other Seeds
